title: AnimoPron: Breaking the Silence(Sound release)
description:
PW: animopron

BREAKING THE QUIET (SOUND RELEASE)



"It was the hardest animation yet - mostly cause of completely custom environments/models. I spend a few months only for combining all things together/rigging characters and so on.

The ending scene is a bit simple, but don't forget that we can't have a cumshot until a "twist". In the last part (2) we'll have at least 2 huge cumshots, and mostly action scenes.

Huge thanks to everyone who is supporting me/supported me. This project was possible ONLY cause of your support. Huge thanks.

There should be a sound version release in a 1,5 weeks here.
Also - there's gonna be "mini-game" release in October as well.

P.S. There's a little bug (1 blank frame) in the video, cause of this AE rendering error. I will re-render it properly tomorrow, and update the links."



Enjoy guys ^_^
